United Air June freight rises 25 % over 1996 . United Airlines transported 25 . 2 percent more freight in June than in the same month a year earlier , the carrier said . Total freight ton miles in June were 194 million , up from 155 million last year . Mail traffic declined 1 . 1 percent , holding the rise in total June cargo to 19 . 2 percent , the carrier said . United ' s strong freight performance this year - first half freight traffic was up 21 percent - reflects several factors , including the addition of four McDonnell Douglas DC - 10 freighters to the Pacific network and the growing number of Boeing 777 twinjets on the Atlantic . - Reuters Air Cargo Service Tel + 44 171 542 7706 Fax + 5017 - www . racs . com 
